lyrics:
[Verse]
We rise against the dark, our voices strong and true
United we stand, in this fight we'll see it through
Against the chains that bind, our spirits free
With every note we sing, our hearts in harmony

[Chorus]
Oh, hear the choir rock, against all odds we thrive
Together we'll break down walls, breaking them with every stride
Oh, the power of our song, against me we'll overcome
In unity we'll rise, until our battle's won
